| MPU6050 Pin | ESP32 Pin             |
| ----------- | --------------------- |
| **VCC**     | **3.3V** ⚠️           |
| **GND**     | **GND**               |
| **SDA**     | **GPIO 4**            |
| **SCL**     | **GPIO 5**            |
| **AD0**     | **GND** (recommended) |
| INT         | Not connected         |


